 2023-01712023-02-16PS
ActExpungement of Historically Unjust Convictions Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the Expungement of Historically Unjust Convictions Act
PrecisOrder Amending the SCHEDULE TO THE EXPUNGEMENT OF HISTORICALLY UNJUST CONVICTIONS ACT in order to make additional historically unjust convictions eligible for expungement, specifically: (1) those related to venues found to be kept for the practice of acts of indecency (e.g., bathhouses, 2SLGBTQI+ nightclubs, swingers clubs); and (2) those related to obtaining, administering, and helping individuals access abortions.
